<IMG SRC="g244370dsp010.jpg" ALT="LOGO">
 </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>SCRIPT</B><B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B></B><B>TITLE:</B> THE SEARCH FOR SCALEABLE SOLUTIONS </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> BIOFUELS </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> R&amp;D UPDATE </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> Dr VIJAY SWARUP </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> Vice President
R&amp;D ExxonMobil </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE: </B>THE BIGGEST CHALLENGE FOR REDUCING EMISSIONS IS SCALE </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> My role is responsible for coordinating the R&amp;D portfolio. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> The biggest challenge with reducing global emissions is one of scale. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> The electrification of cars and light duty vehicles is going to play a big role.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>
</DIV></Center>


<p style="margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:0em; page-break-before:always">
<HR SIZE="3" style="COLOR:#999999" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">


<Center><DIV STYLE="width:8.5in" align="left">
 <P STYLE="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> ELECTRIC VEHICLES ARE A COMPONENT </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> The electric vehicle is a component of a system that has&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> OF A SYSTEM THAT HAS SCALABLE ENERGY WITH LOWER EMISSIONS <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> scalable energy with lower emissions. <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> But there&#146;s going to be a point where energy density is needed.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> BUT WE ALSO NEED LOWER CARBON FUELS <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> So what you&#146;re going to be looking for is lower-carbon fuels.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> We are looking at biofuels: algae and cellulosic. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> WE ARE LOOKING AT BIOFUELS ALGAE AND CELLULOSIC </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> Next-generation fuels. </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> FOR AIRPLANES,
TRUCKS AND SHIPS </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> And that&#146;s for airplanes, that&#146;s for large trucks, that&#146;s for ships. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> It has to be scalable and globally deployable. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> ALGAE CAN BE SCALED </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> Algae grows in
brackish water, so it&#146;s not competing for land for food. </P> <P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> IT DOESN&#146;T COMPETE FOR LAND FOR GROWING FOOD </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> Or for water that&#146;s used for irrigation. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> CELLULOSIC MATERIAL IS AGRICULTURAL MATERIAL LEFTOVER AFTER THE HARVEST </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> Cellulosic material, which is agricultural waste, if you will. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> The material that&#146;s left after you&#146;ve harvested the food. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> That has potential to also provide biofuels. </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> Those two together could provide the <FONT STYLE="white-space:nowrap">low-emission</FONT> fuels&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> for the transportation sector.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>
</DIV></Center>


<p style="margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:0em; page-break-before:always">
<HR SIZE="3" style="COLOR:#999999" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">


<Center><DIV STYLE="width:8.5in" align="left">
 <P STYLE="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> EXXONMOBIL HAS A LONG HISTORY OF PROVIDING SCALEABLE SOLUTIONS </P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ</B><B>:</B> We have a long history of being providers of scalable solutions,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TI</B><B>TLE: </B>UNDERPINNING MANY OF THE ADVANCES SOCIETY HAS HAD IN ENERGY <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>VJ:</B> which have really underpinned a lot of the advances society has had in energy. <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE:</B> FOLLOW OUR PROGRESS ON SOLVING THE DUAL CHALLENGE <B> </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>TITLE</B><B>:</B> (ENERGY FACTOR LOGO)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>
</DIV></Center>


<p style="margin-top:1em; margin-bottom:0em; page-break-before:always">
<HR SIZE="3" style="COLOR:#999999" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">

 <P STYLE="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman"><B>Important Additional Information Regarding Proxy Solicitation </B></P>
<P STYLE="margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:Times New Roman">Exxon Mobil Corporation (&#147;ExxonMobil&#148;) has filed a definitive proxy statement and form of associated BLUE proxy card with the U.S. Securities and
Exchange Commission (the &#147;SEC&#148;) in connection with the solicitation of proxies for ExxonMobil&#146;s 2021 Annual Meeting (the &#147;Proxy Statement&#148;). ExxonMobil, its directors and certain of its executive officers will be
participants in the solicitation of proxies from shareholders in respect of the 2021 Annual Meeting. Information regarding the names of ExxonMobil&#146;s directors and executive officers and their respective interests in ExxonMobil by security
holdings or otherwise is set forth in the Proxy Statement. To the extent holdings of such participants in ExxonMobil&#146;s securities are not reported, or have changed since the amounts described, in the Proxy Statement, such changes have been
reflected on Initial Statements of Beneficial Ownership on Form 3 or Statements of Change in Ownership on Form 4 filed with the SEC. Details concerning the nominees of ExxonMobil&#146;s Board of Directors for election at the 2021 Annual Meeting are
included in the Proxy Statement. BEFORE MAKING ANY VOTING DECISION, INVESTORS AND SHAREHOLDERS OF THE COMPANY ARE URGED TO READ ALL RELEVANT DOCUMENTS FILED WITH OR FURNISHED TO THE SEC, INCLUDING THE COMPANY&#146;S DEFINITIVE PROXY STATEMENT AND
ANY SUPPLEMENTS THERETO AND ACCOMPANYING BLUE PROXY CARD, BECAUSE THEY CONTAIN IMPORTANT INFORMATION. Investors and shareholders can obtain a copy of the Proxy Statement and other relevant documents filed by ExxonMobil free of charge from the
SEC&#146;s website, www.sec.gov. ExxonMobil&#146;s shareholders can also obtain, without charge, a copy of the Proxy Statement and other relevant filed documents by directing a request by mail to ExxonMobil Shareholder Services at 5959 Las Colinas
Boulevard, Irving, Texas, 75039-2298 or at shareholderrelations@exxonmobil.com or from the investor relations section of ExxonMobil&#146;s website, www.exxonmobil.com/investor. </P>
